data.description: Come see this wonderful home in Ryan Ridge! Beautiful hard wood floors throughout the home with tile in the kitchen, laundry room and bathrooms. The layout includes four bedrooms, two full baths and one half bath with trey ceilings in the living room and master bedroom. Lovely chandeliers in both the living room and dining room. The master walk-in closet is huge and the walk-in closets in the other bedrooms have french doors. The eat in kitchen has tile back splash and a bar that will seat four.  There are wood blinds throughout the home and the interior has just been freshly painted.  The house is light and airy with a fully fenced back yard and a covered patio.
